Alembic migrations for github-issue-pr-agent.

The schema (agent_runs, audit_entries) is also created automatically at runtime
via DatabaseManager.create_tables() when the database is reachable, so the agent
runs with no manual migration step. These migrations exist for production-style
deployments that prefer explicit, versioned schema management.

Apply migrations:   alembic upgrade head
Create a revision:  alembic revision --autogenerate -m "message"
